---
// BeforeAfter — split panel showing raw sensationalist post vs Devoke's calm rewrite.
// Left: slightly red-tinted surface, aggressive typography styling.
// Right: clean, green-tinted, airy.
// A thin green rule divides them. The same event is described both ways.
---

<section class="ba section" id="before-after" aria-label="Before and after comparison">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-label reveal">What it does</span>
    <h2 class="ba__heading reveal">Same story. Different signal.</h2>
    <p class="ba__sub reveal">
      Devoke doesn't remove anything. It strips the manipulation — then gets out of the way.
    </p>

    <div class="ba__panels reveal">
      <!-- Before panel -->
      <div class="ba__panel ba__panel--before" role="region" aria-label="Before Devoke — original sensationalist post">
        <div class="ba__panel-label">
          <span class="ba__dot ba__dot--red" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          Original
        </div>
        <blockquote class="ba__post ba__post--before">
          <p>
            This CORRUPT politician just DESTROYED the economy and nobody is talking
            about it!! The mainstream media is HIDING THE TRUTH — share before
            they take this down!! 🔥🔥🔥
          </p>
        </blockquote>
        <div class="ba__meta ba__meta--before">
          <span>48.2K likes</span>
          <span>12.1K reposts</span>
          <span>3.4M views</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Divider -->
      <div class="ba__divider" aria-hidden="true">
        <span class="ba__divider-mark">◎</span>
      </div>

      <!-- After panel -->
      <div class="ba__panel ba__panel--after" role="region" aria-label="After Devoke — rewritten calm version">
        <div class="ba__panel-label">
          <span class="ba__dot ba__dot--green" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          Devoke
        </div>
        <blockquote class="ba__post ba__post--after">
          <p>
            A politician faces accusations of economic mismanagement.
            Coverage of this story has been limited in some major outlets.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
        <div class="ba__meta ba__meta--after">
          <span class="ba__hidden-label">Metrics hidden</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="ba__footnote reveal">
      The toggle button <span class="ba__mark-inline" aria-hidden="true">◎</span> appears on every rewritten post — tap it to see the original at any time.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .ba {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    clip-path: var(--clip-full);
    margin-block: -2px; /* prevent subpixel gaps */
  }

  .ba__heading {
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .ba__sub {
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }

  /* Panels layout */
  .ba__panels {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid rgba(122, 184, 138, 0.12);
    max-width: 900px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .ba__panels {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      grid-template-rows: 1fr auto 1fr;
    }
  }

  /* Panel base */
  .ba__panel {
    padding: 2rem 2.2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.2rem;
  }

  .ba__panel--before {
    background: rgba(196, 117, 106, 0.06);
  }

  .ba__panel--after {
    background: rgba(122, 184, 138, 0.05);
  }

  /* Label row */
  .ba__panel-label {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .ba__dot {
    width: 7px;
    height: 7px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .ba__dot--red   { background: var(--color-red); }
  .ba__dot--green { background: var(--color-green); }

  /* Post text */
  .ba__post {
    flex: 1;
    margin: 0;
    border: none;
  }

  .ba__post p {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.97rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    max-width: 100%;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  /* Before-specific: tighter, more aggressive feel */
  .ba__post--before p {
    color: rgba(184, 212, 190, 0.75);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  /* After: clean, green-leaning */
  .ba__post--after p {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Meta row */
  .ba__meta {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .ba__meta--after {
    color: var(--color-green-dim);
  }

  .ba__hidden-label {
    font-style: italic;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  /* Divider */
  .ba__divider {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 1px;
    background: rgba(122, 184, 138, 0.25);
    position: relative;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .ba__divider {
      width: 100%;
      height: 1px;
      padding: 0;
    }
  }

  .ba__divider-mark {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-green);
    background: var(--color-surface);
    padding: 0.25rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  /* Footnote */
  .ba__footnote {
    margin-top: 1.8rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 100%;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .ba__mark-inline {
    color: var(--color-green);
    font-style: normal;
  }
</style>
